2002-1042 (La. 9/18/02)

In re Tony T. LE. No. 2002-OB-1042. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Sept. 18, 2002.

In re Le, Tony T.; —Plaintiff; Applying for Petition to Appoint a Commissioner.

ORDER

Considering the report and recommendation of the Commissioner,

*1122IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that petitioner’s application for admission to the practice of law be and hereby is dismissed without prejudice.
